    "_help": [
        "=== LumaFader Settings ===",
        "",
        "CHANNELS: Set as number (1) or string. Use pipe for multi-channel: 1|2|3",
        "  <blank>  = inherit from parent (slider -> bank -> page -> global)",
        "  GLOBAL   = use global channel directly",
        "  PAGE     = use page channel (bank settings only)",
        "",
        "MESSAGE TYPES: CC (Control Change) or AT (Channel Aftertouch)",
        "  CC = sends CC messages using the CC numbers in the page arrays",
        "  AT = sends aftertouch pressure (CC numbers ignored, one value per channel)",
        "",
        "GLOBAL_SLIDER_CHANNELS: Per-slider channel overrides for the global bank.",
        "  Each entry corresponds to a slider (A, B, C, D). Blank = use GLOBAL_CHANNEL.",
        "",
        "PAGE_N_BANK_SLIDER_CHANNELS: Per-slider channel overrides within each bank.",
        "  Outer array = bank (0-3), inner array = slider (A-D). Blank = use bank channel.",
        "",
        "Tip: Avoid overlapping channels between pages for best pickup mode behavior."
